					Amount Allocated $0


					Amount remaining in monthly budget $0





Step 3 of 4
The Future-Haves
Weʼll fill in the rest of your monthly budget for you by setting aside money for tomorrow: your retirement contributions, building an emergency fund, paying off credit card debt and more.


 The percentages you selected for each budget category are: 
10% Must-Haves
10% Nice-to-Haves
80% Future-Haves







