Access your accounts

Pursuing your goals is a process. That’s why we offer an online experience that gives you transparent access to all your investments.






Track your progress





Track your progress

View your investments in the context of reaching your goal. Always know how far you've come, and how far you have to go, with probability indicators letting you know how likely you are to reach your goal along the way.






Get ideas





Get ideas

TD Ameritrade Investment Management proactively makes suggestions if you start to veer from reaching your goals. From timeline tweaks to contribution changes, we show you the most impactful actions to help you keep your portfolio on track.



















Smart people. Our most valuable asset.
From the professionals at Morningstar Investment Management, to the team at TD Ameritrade Investment Management who monitor and rebalance the portfolios, to the portfolio specialists who answer your calls and questions — real people are with you every step of the way. Call 866-551-6917 to get started with Selective Portfolios today.












Invest on the go with the TD Ameritrade Portfolios App


See how well your portfolio is doing by monitoring the performance of your past and projected investments. View your account balances and asset allocations to know when you'll reach your target.


















